apache::minimal optional variables:
  $log_format - access log format, or nickname, as the CustomLog directive takes
    (default: common)
apache::basic and apache::ssl::basic optional variables:
  $http_listen_address - interface on which httpd should listen (default: *,
    meaning all interfaces)
apache::redirecting optional variables:
  $canonical_www_name - canonical name to which non-matching HTTP requests
    should be redirected (default: $fqdn)
